channel.title: Webclient Won't Log Anyone In Help!
channel.description: Can someone please help me? I have a server that says its online and I put it on rsps coding. It loads up fine and everything, but doesnt log anyone in. It says " Error Connecting, please try again in 1 min". So can somebody please help me? It would be appreciated. Thanks

item.title: Webclient Won't Log Anyone In Help!
item.dc:creator: @Sagi Sagi
item.description:
@Sagi wrote:

Probably IP/Client ID problem. Have you set the right IP for the webclient you made?
